    "10: end for 11: Truncate S to its first m entries, and release.Connection to Gray codes.",
    "From the perspective of Gray codes, our pseudorandom bit generation scheme can be viewed as a special case of a 2-Gray code.",
    "We present the formal construction process below.Let n ∈ N. Denote by {0, 1} n the set of all binary strings of length n, and by d H (•, •) the Hamming distance on {0, 1} n. Let G n = (g n 0, g n 1,..., g n 2 n -1) with g n i ∈ {0, 1} n be a standard n-bit 1-Gray code, specified up to cyclic permutation.",
